OL,5, Carol Vorderman has promised to "cause 
OL,6, a commotion" as the host of a new LBC  
OL,7, show.                                  
OL,9,FThe former Countdown star left her     
OL,10,Fweekly BBC Radio Wales programme in    
OL,11,FNovember after breaking BBC guidelines 
OL,12,Fwith vocal attacks against the         
OL,13,Fgovernment on social media.            
OL,15,FShe said she was "not prepared to lose 
OL,16,Fmy voice" after the BBC introduced new 
OL,17,Fsocial media guidelines.               
OL,19,FVorderman will host her three-hour     
OL,20,Fprogramme on LBC every Sunday.         
